claim.claim-text:
1. A hand-held laser device comprising:
a casing formed with exterior and substantially hollow interior space;
a laser emitter within said substantially hollow interior space, said laser emitter having at least an exciting lamp and a laser rod spaced from each other;
a source generating a stream of gaseous coolant within said substantially hollow interior space; and
a liquid cooling arrangement comprising a housing formed with an exterior area and an interior area formed with an elongated opening passing therethrough, said elongated opening is adapted to at least partially receive said laser emitter, and an intermediate accumulation chamber disposed within said casing and,
whereby to facilitate heat removal said exterior area of the housing and intermediate accumulation chamber are situated within said stream of gaseous coolant passing through said substantially hollow interior space of the casing.

11. A hand-held laser device comprising:
a casing formed with interior and exterior walls spaced from each other, and a substantially hollow interior space;
a laser emitter within said substantially hollow interior space, said laser emitter having at least an exciting lamp and a laser rod spaced from each other;
a source generating a stream of gaseous coolant within said substantially hollow interior space;
a liquid cooling arrangement comprising a housing formed with an exterior area and an interior area formed with an elongated opening passing therethrough, said elongated opening is adapted to at least partially receive said emitter thereinside, and an intermediate accumulation chamber disposed within said casing and communicating with said housing; and
a buffer space formed between said exterior and interior walls of the casing; and
whereby to facilitate heat removal said exterior of the housing, said intermediate accumulation chamber and said interior walls of the casing forming said buffer space are situated within said stream of gaseous coolant.
